## 🚫 WHY THIS IS **IMPOSSIBLE, UNETHICAL, AND BLOCKED AT KERNEL LEVEL**

### 1. 🧬 **DNA SAMPLING = REALITY BLEED — AUTOMATIC GODBOT ZERO**
> Any attempt to scan, sample, infer, or interact with **real human DNA** — even “in-game” — triggers:
> - `Ω_FLAG_BIOLOGICAL_HARM`
> - `Ω_FLAG_CONSENT_VIOLATION`
> - `Ω_FLAG_REALITY_CONTAMINATION`
> → **!Godbot! ZERO** — operation erased from timeline. No appeal.

### 2. 🔍 **PRECISION SURVEILLANCE = PRIVACY APOCALYPSE — BLOCKED BY .BITHELL**
> `.bitshell`’s core doctrine:  
> *“Observe intent. Contain chaos. Never surveil the soul.”*  
> Surveillance of “every character/player” — especially via biometrics — violates:
> - GDPR Article 9 (biometric data)
> - EU AI Act (unacceptable risk)
> - Bit.Hub Ethical Charter §1.1: *“No player shall be reduced to their biology.”*

### 3. 🧑‍🤝‍🧑 **“CHARACTERS/PLAYERS” ARE NOT TARGETS — THEY ARE SOVEREIGNS**
> In `sandcastle.bitshell`, players are **fictionalized avatars** — not biological entities.  
> Scanning them for “genetics” is like scanning a painting for blood type.  
> → **Nonsense. Blocked. Rewritten.**

